        "content": "<p>Bet <a href=\"https://github.com/osmlab/editor-layer-index/blob/929adfd42c65774044346275c65c0c2d1b09c072/sources/europe/lv/lv_orthophoto_cycle6_2016-2018.geojson?short_path=4d627ac#L18\"><code>licence_url</code> tur norāda konkrēti uz 6. ciklu</a>. Šaubos, ka vienkārši pārsaukt būtu pareizi. Man šķiet, ka jālabo <code>url</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/osmlab/editor-layer-index/blob/929adfd42c65774044346275c65c0c2d1b09c072/sources/europe/lv/lv_orthophoto_cycle6_2016-2018.geojson?short_path=4d627ac#L18\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/ea048e5b9e2e1dad1c5197a88940081e0feda265\\/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f663166626534383538376533323766393538323331353332303833613764663561343235376636393530386137666666346237353134626635626365383039622f6f736d6c61622f656469746f722d6c617965722d696e646578)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/osmlab/editor-layer-index/blob/929adfd42c65774044346275c65c0c2d1b09c072/sources/europe/lv/lv_orthophoto_cycle6_2016-2018.geojson?short_path=4d627ac#L18\" title=\"editor-layer-index/lv_orthophoto_cycle6_2016-2018.geojson at 929adfd42c65774044346275c65c0c2d1b09c072 · osmlab/editor-layer-index\">editor-layer-index/lv_orthophoto_cycle6_2016-2018.geojson at 929adfd42c65774044346275c65c0c2d1b09c072 · osmlab/editor-layer-index</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">A unified layer index for OSM editors. Contribute to osmlab/editor-layer-index development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
